            "tool_use_id": "toolu_e750ebfe05e14e19b65cf9f7",
            "type": "tool_result",
            "content": "1→#!/bin/zsh\n     2→\n     3→# Claude 完整上下文信息提取脚本\n     4→# 功能：完整记录 Claude 对话的全部上下文信息，包括工具调用、完整消息内容等\n     5→\n     6→PROJECT=$(pwd | sed 's/\\//-/g')\n     7→LATEST=\"${1:-$(ls -t ~/.claude/projects/$PROJECT/*.jsonl 2>/dev/null | head -1)}\"\n     8→\n     9→# 检查文件是否存在\n    10→if [[ -z \"$LATEST\" ]]; then\n    11→    echo \"错误: 未找到会话文件\"\n    12→    echo \"请确保在正确的项目目录下执行此脚本\"\n    13→    exit 1\n    14→fi\n    15→\n    16→echo \"=== Claude 完整对话上下文 ===\"\n    17→echo \"会话文件: $LATEST\"\n    18→echo \"生成时间: $(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\"\n    19→echo \"================================\"\n    20→echo\n    21→\n    22→# 使用 jq 完整解析并显示所有信息\n    23→cat \"$LATEST\" | jq -r '\n    24→def format_timestamp:\n    25→  if .timestamp then\n    26→    \"[\" + (.timestamp[0:19] | gsub(\"T\";\" \")) + \"]\"\n    27→  else\n    28→    \"[未知时间]\"\n    29→  end;\n    30→\n    31→def format_message_type:\n    32→  (.type // \"unknown\" | ascii_upcase);\n    33→\n    34→def format_user_content:\n    35→  if .message.content then\n    36→    if .message.content | type == \"string\" then\n    37→      .message.content\n    38→    elif .message.content | type == \"array\" then\n    39→      .message.content | map(\n    40→        if .type == \"text\" then\n    41→          .text\n    42→        elif .type == \"tool_use\" then\n    43→          \"[工具调用] \" + (.name // \"unknown\") + \": \" + (.input | tostring)\n    44→        else\n    45→          \"[类型: \" + (.type // \"unknown\") + \"] \" + (.text // .content // \"\")\n    46→        end\n    47→      ) | join(\"\\n\")\n    48→    else\n    49→      .message.content | tostring\n    50→    end\n    51→  else\n    52→    \"[空内容]\"\n    53→  end;\n    54→\n    55→def format_assistant_content:\n    56→  if .message.content then\n    57→    if .message.content | type == \"string\" then\n    58→      .message.content\n    59→    elif .message.content | type == \"array\" then\n    60→      .message.content | map(\n    61→        if .type == \"text\" then\n    62→          .text\n    63→        elif .type == \"tool_use\" then\n    64→          \"[工具调用] \" + (.name // \"unknown\") + \"\\n输入参数: \" + (.input | tojson)\n    65→        elif .type == \"tool_result\" then\n    66→          \"[工具结果] ID: \" + (.tool_use_id // \"unknown\") + \"\\n结果: \" + (.content // \"\" | tostring)\n    67→        else\n    68→          \"[类型: \" + (.type // \"unknown\") + \"] \" + (.text // .content // \"\" | tostring)\n    69→        end\n    70→      ) | join(\"\\n---\\n\")\n    71→    else\n    72→      .message.content | tostring\n    73→    end\n    74→  else\n    75→    \"[无回复内容]\"\n    76→  end;\n    77→\n    78→def format_system_content:\n    79→  if .message.content then\n    80→    .message.content | tostring\n    81→  else\n    82→    \"[系统消息]\"\n    83→  end;\n    84→\n    85→# 主处理逻辑\n    86→select(.type != null) |\n    87→format_timestamp + \" \" + format_message_type + \":\\n\" +\n    88→(\n    89→  if .type == \"user\" then\n    90→    format_user_content\n    91→  elif .type == \"assistant\" then\n    92→    format_assistant_content\n    93→  elif .type == \"system\" then\n    94→    format_system_content\n    95→  else\n    96→    \"[未知类型: \" + (.type // \"null\") + \"] 内容: \" + (.message.content // \"\" | tostring)\n    97→  end\n    98→) + \"\\n\" + \"=\"*50 + \"\\n\"\n    99→'\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n\n<system-reminder>\nCRITICAL: This is a READ-ONLY task. You CANNOT edit, write, or create files.\n</system-reminder>"
